```python
import pandas as pd

df_stock = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": ["A"]*7 + ["B"]*7,
    "day":   [1,2,3,4,5,6,7]*2,
    "stock": [20,15,8,5,3,12,18,   25,22,19,10,4,2,15]
})

df_threshold = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": ["A","B"],
    "min_stock": [10, 8]
})
display(df_stock, df_threshold)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_merged = df_stock.merge(df_threshold, how='left', on='store')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['is_oos']=df_merged['stock']<df_merged['min_stock']
display(df_merged)
g = df_merged.groupby('store')
prev = g['is_oos'].shift(1, fill_value=False)
nxt = g['is_oos'].shift(-1, fill_value=False)
df_merged['oos_session_id'] = (df_merged['is_oos']&~prev).groupby(df_merged['store']).cumsum()
display(df_merged)
streak = (df_merged[df_merged['is_oos']]
          .groupby(['store','oos_session_id'])
          .size()
          .reset_index(name='streak_len'))
display(streak)
max_streak = (streak.groupby('store', as_index=False)['streak_len'].max()
              .rename(columns={'streak_len':'max_oos_streak'}))
store_feat = df_merged.groupby('store').agg(
    oos_days = ('is_oos', 'sum'),  
).reset_index()
store_feat=store_feat.merge(max_streak, how='left', on='store')
display(store_feat)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=2, ncols=1, figsize=(7,6))
stores = ['A', 'B']
for idx, store in enumerate(stores):
    r = df_merged[df_merged['store']==store]
    r_scatter = df_merged[(df_merged['store']==store)&(df_merged['is_oos'])]
    axes[idx].plot(r['day'],r['stock'])
    axes[idx].plot(r['day'],r['min_stock'], color='gray', linestyle='--')
    axes[idx].scatter(r_scatter['day'], r_scatter['stock'], color='red')
    axes[idx].set_title(f'Store {store} Stock Trend')
    axes[idx].set_xlabel('day')
    axes[idx].set_ylabel('stock')
    axes[idx].grid(False)
plt.show()
```
